{"type":"answer","id":111619,"parentType":"question","parentId":8915,"uid":21366,"contents":"作者：知乎用户<br>\n链接：https://www.zhihu.com/question/19609089/answer/213666306<br>\n来源：知乎<br>\n著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。<br>\n<br>\n这篇回答专注推荐答主本人<b>在YouTube上发掘到的优秀的电影类博主/账号</b>，他们的存在让我觉得油管真是一个非常适合自学者的巨大宝库。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n按内容可以分为三类：<br>\n<br>\n第一类是<b>拉片/分析/影评类</b>，常常以某种电影类型、某位导演或某种表现手法为主题，通过详尽的拉片+解读来输出知识、论证观点；<br>\n<br>\n第二类是<b>影迷向的“营销号”</b>，常有每周固定的排行榜和影史盘点类节目，以及丰富的电影花絮/周边/影人访谈放送；<br>\n<br>\n第三类是<b>电影制作教学类账号</b>，从前期到后期的各种“how-to”基本上都能找到，对想自己拍电影的人来说是很好的手把手教学的资源。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>一、拉片/分析/影评类</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>1 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UCL5kBJmBUVFLYBDiSiK1VDw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Channel Criswell</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-605d08a70123a0976083842dc40089f3_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-605d08a70123a0976083842dc40089f3_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-605d08a70123a0976083842dc40089f3_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-605d08a70123a0976083842dc40089f3_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n重点推荐的第一个账号，由现居加拿大的英国电影人Lewis Bond独立运营。主打时长为15-20分钟的视频论文，内容分为Directors/Video Essays/In Storytelling/Analysis Videos/Movie Reviews这几类，其中Directors系列下已有对<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D52raDbtNpa4%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">宫崎骏</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D2G7oeyOsfSg%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">小津安二郎</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DLCG2nuM3RFw%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">库布里克</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3Dak6rI-j07QU%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">塔可夫斯基</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3Dxwhe1zDHrCQ%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">拉斯·冯·特里尔</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D2mhwQdV2iYQ%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">大卫·林奇</a>、<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DY3ctpzJ2BeE%26list%3DPLsZPlgdMyS8DDiVOKDh0lt58FCPnDhhN0%26index%3D7%26t%3D111s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">阿基·考里斯马基</a>的分析视频，他对这些导演风格的概括在标题里就有体现：<br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-17c5f9723bee1b3a50995714ad3b94f2_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;384&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;508&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;384&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-17c5f9723bee1b3a50995714ad3b94f2_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-17c5f9723bee1b3a50995714ad3b94f2_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-17c5f9723bee1b3a50995714ad3b94f2_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\nVideo Essays类中，则有诸如“<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DBQEv3PzuO2c\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《自己来看》的视听语言</a>”，“<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D0R7R0JHvvgo\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">法国新浪潮对规则的突破</a>”，“<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3DJ3nXrU0c2JA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《老男孩》与希腊悲剧</a>”，“<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3Do0DotIqOD-E%26t%3D114s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《十二宫杀手》和《杀人回忆》的比较分析</a>”等有趣的题目，还有一期时长46分钟的<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/watch%3Fv%3D0cryX-ZU1h0%26t%3D22s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">对恐怖片的全面论述</a>。<br>\n<br>\n总体来说，他的视频学术性强，论述精准，角度全面，非常值得一看。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>2 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/everyframeapainting\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Every Frame A Painting</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-79c2f6c826bc9b389f757f9069610cc1_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-79c2f6c826bc9b389f757f9069610cc1_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-79c2f6c826bc9b389f757f9069610cc1_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-79c2f6c826bc9b389f757f9069610cc1_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n应该是油管最火的影评类账号了，订阅人数超过120万。同样主打视频论文，内容主要按照影人来组织，上学期IMBd的放映活动中我们就放了他的“今敏的时空剪辑”和“剪辑师是如何思考的”两期内容。 幕后作者Tony Zhou主业就是剪辑师，评论的角度很专业，视频做得也干脆利落，一期3-9分钟视频的干货量胜过很多长篇大论的影评。不过悲催的是，他似乎已经有10个月没更新了。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>3 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UCWTFGPpNQ0Ms6afXhaWDiRw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Now You See It</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-09034db2217c966062c753109c19cf85_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-09034db2217c966062c753109c19cf85_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-09034db2217c966062c753109c19cf85_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-09034db2217c966062c753109c19cf85_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n又一个有趣的电影分析类账号，简介里的自我定位是“一门大学电影分析课，不含教室、作业和学费贷款”。它的独特之处在于，选题的切入点通常较小，比如“滑动变焦的功效”、“棋类运动/牛奶道具/骂人台词在电影里的意义”、“恐怖片里的跳接”等等，而分析时则以大量经典影片为例证，可以说是优秀论文的写作思路了。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>同类推荐</b>：<br>\n<br>\n<b>4 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UCVjsbqKtxkLt7bal4NWRjJQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ScreenPrism</a></b>：一个视频制作精良的影视知识普及营销号，内容通俗易懂，有对各种电影/剧集的剧情、人物、手法、象征符号的分析和拆解。干货是有的，但相对较浅。<br>\n<br>\n<b>5 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UC7GV-3hrA9kDKrren0QMKMg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CinemaTyler</a></b>：谈论从影史经典中获得的启发，标题常用句式为“What ... movie teaches us about filmmaking”<br>\n<br>\n<b>6 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/YourMovieSucksDOTorg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">YourMovieSucksDOTorg</a></b> : 大部分时间专注于北美新片吐槽，偶有长篇系列影评（最初关注是因为他做了五期《纽约提喻法》的拉片，总时长快赶上电影本身长度了）<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>二、影迷向</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>7 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/screenjunkies\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Screen Junkies</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-4098ab496922a457a12e7da82fc17aef_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-4098ab496922a457a12e7da82fc17aef_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-4098ab496922a457a12e7da82fc17aef_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-4098ab496922a457a12e7da82fc17aef_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n大名鼎鼎的“诚实预告片”系列的始作俑者，650万粉丝的油管最红频道之一。其实它的内容非常丰富，有很多直播栏目和影迷对谈，可以概括为一个略偏宅向的film geeks大本营。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>8 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/CineFix\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CineFix</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f30b170ce8113da7de63f8a4106902d0_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f30b170ce8113da7de63f8a4106902d0_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f30b170ce8113da7de63f8a4106902d0_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f30b170ce8113da7de63f8a4106902d0_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n拥有超过250万粉丝的老牌影迷向营销号，每周都有固定的几大栏目更新，最热门的栏目包括各类“十大”盘点、“你不知道的7件事”花絮系列、“8bit预告片”系列等等。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>9 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/10ThingsYouDidntKnow\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AlltimeMovies</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-1cceb7cdd775ec8e699bd38d6727be06_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-1cceb7cdd775ec8e699bd38d6727be06_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-1cceb7cdd775ec8e699bd38d6727be06_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-1cceb7cdd775ec8e699bd38d6727be06_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n另一个主打花样繁多琳琅满目的电影盘点视频的营销号，除了各种“十大”，更有趣的是“Every Reference”系列，顾名思义就是找出某作品中出现的所有梗和典故，非常影迷向。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>同类推荐：</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>10 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UCEl1uPV2NjW0xzceOth7Hbw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">BryceMakesFilms</a></b>：主要内容是对热门影片的剧情解析，以及挖掘预告片中观众注意不到的细节。<br>\n<br>\n<b>11 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/channel/UCfeblC3PfVe_ORV4bBKYfDQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">The Narrative Art</a></b>：海量导演和编剧访谈。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>三、电影制作教学类</b><br>\n<br>\n<b>12 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/filmriot\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Film Riot</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-35b8e5f3684f844d5522c84c053be1d6_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-35b8e5f3684f844d5522c84c053be1d6_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-35b8e5f3684f844d5522c84c053be1d6_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-35b8e5f3684f844d5522c84c053be1d6_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n油管上历史最悠久（11年） 的拍电影教学账号，也是内容最丰富的一个，基本上你能想到的关于拍电影的方方面面它都有涉及：剧本写作、摄影、器材、布光、道具、叙事手法、剪辑、特效合成，还有对院线电影幕后拍摄的讲解……曾经用它教的手法实验过一些有趣的小片段，非常实用。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>13 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/FilmmakerIQcom\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Filmmaker IQ</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-578917ac845f19e5e568ed0c1628cdec_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-578917ac845f19e5e568ed0c1628cdec_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-578917ac845f19e5e568ed0c1628cdec_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-578917ac845f19e5e568ed0c1628cdec_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n真·提纯干货，老师用小黑板讲解电影技术的方方面面，平均时长20分钟以上，相当于一门正式的公开课了。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>14 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/RJFilmSchool\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">RocketJump Film School</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-5897cae4b8b2b5b3aa58f62591a4de70_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5897cae4b8b2b5b3aa58f62591a4de70_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5897cae4b8b2b5b3aa58f62591a4de70_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5897cae4b8b2b5b3aa58f62591a4de70_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n一个专业的在线电影教学账号，有自己的网站。涉及的内容和Film Riot相仿，除此之外还有一些业界人士的专访和经典电影的分析。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>15 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/YapperDesign\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Cinecom.net</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a51347b30b910af61d9b91fb8d22a755_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a51347b30b910af61d9b91fb8d22a755_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a51347b30b910af61d9b91fb8d22a755_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-a51347b30b910af61d9b91fb8d22a755_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n强调“创意电影拍摄教学”，注重摄影、剪辑、调色等纯技术类的教程，包括一些设备和软件的用法等等。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>16 <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.youtube.com/user/DSLRguide\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">DSLRguide</a></b><br>\n<br>\n&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-39b6fc48c63e0086209b7ce06f96a0d7_hd.jpg&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;100&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;100&quot; class=&quot;content_image&quot; width=&quot;100&quot;/&gt;<a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-39b6fc48c63e0086209b7ce06f96a0d7_hd.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-39b6fc48c63e0086209b7ce06f96a0d7_hd.jpg\" alt=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-39b6fc48c63e0086209b7ce06f96a0d7_hd.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n顾名思义，它的教程围绕着“用单反拍电影”，引申来说就是如何让业余爱好者拍出更有电影感的画面——在这个一以贯之的主题下，进行一些技术类窍门的指导和普及。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n以上就是我在YouTube上关注的全部电影类账号了。个人觉得，无论广度还是深度，每一类账号的质量都能完爆大部分国内同类新媒体平台，让人不禁感叹一堵墙隔开了多少东西，又让多少人得以蒙混过关。","date":"2019-12-23","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}